Ol_a_-ika alla_th_eena anAAama All_a_hu AAalayhim mina a*l*nnabiyyeena min _th_urriyyati _a_dama wamimman _h_amaln_a_ maAAa noo_h_in wamin _th_urriyyati ibr_a_heema wa-isr_a_-eela wamimman hadayn_a_ wa*i*jtabayn_a_ i_tha_ tutl_a_ AAalayhim _a_y_a_tu a*l*rra_h_m_a_ni kharroo sujjadan wabukiyy_a_*n*
